snippet.title: Super Mario World. U | December Trailer [Unofficial Mod]
snippet.description:
Super Mario World. U is a NSMBU mod that contains a bunch of new adventures for our beloved Mario! This mod will be single player only and will have 6 worlds to explore. Everything showcased in this trailer is under development so please, don't be afraid to make suggestions! All feedback will be appreciated.

There is no release date for now. I want to take all the time the mod needs to satisfy all of my ideas. Be patient! You'll find more development updates on:
· SMWU discord's server: https://discord.gg/EMVbfU49hX

Please, visit SMWU Gamebanana page for more information and credits along special thanks to people who have been esential for the development:
· SMWU Gamebanana page: https://gamebanana.com/wips/74649

Special thanks to Gale Sosa and her friend MistyRockandRoll for making this beautiful trailer music.

Merry Christmas! 🎄♡
